# 📊 Product Sales Dashboard (Excel)

## 📌 Project Overview
This project showcases an interactive Product Sales Dashboard built in Microsoft Excel. It demonstrates data analysis and dashboard creation using Pivot Tables, Pivot Charts, KPIs, XLOOKUP, and Slicers.

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Pivot Charts
- XLOOKUP
- KPI Cards
- Slicers
- Excel Tables

---

## 📈 Dashboard KPIs
- Total Products
- Total Stock Quantity
- Average Price
- Highest Price
- Lowest Price
- Average Score

---

## 📊 Dashboard Features
- Interactive Category Slicer
- Product Distribution Pie Chart
- Stock Quantity by Category
- Average Price by Category
- Dynamic KPI Cards

